snippet.title: Mario Artist: Paint Studio (Nintendo 64DD 1999)
snippet.description: Bulk footage of the Mario Artist: Pain Studio software for Nintendo 64DD. This video has footage of most of the softwares features as well as a few minutes of the Nintendo 64 DD Bios Screen. This footage is free to use as well as proper credit is given.
